Operations executed on current SVN trunk or specific branches:

dynamic.sh:
 Script which calls create-ggzpots.sh and statistics-ggzpos.sh

create-ggzpots.sh:
 Tarball with all *.pot file for download
 (and the properties files for ggz-java)

statistics-art.sh:
 What kind of graphics and how many of each do we have?

statistics-ggzpos.sh:
 How many catalogs are translated for each language?

statistics-webpages.sh:
 How many webpages are translated?

generate-branch-diffs.sh:
 Generate diff files for modifications on a branch

The generated files are then installed into the dev/ section of the
webpage, and used by the PHP scripts to display some statistics.

